reviews.review: Beautiful Film!!! Love every minute of it. The story, the animation, and the amazing score. Beautiful songs! I just love it!!!

Filmnya sangat memukau akan keindahan hutan, istana, dan terutama salju dan esnya elsa sehingga sangat layak untuk di tonton, selain itu alur ceritanya sangat kompleks lebih mengarah ke cerita magis dan dewasa. Lalu film ini juga mengisahkan asal usul kekuatan Elsa dan ketiadaan orang tuanya Elsa, sehingga film ini sebagai jawaban di semua pertanyaan film seri pertamanya dan sangat layak untuk ditonton.
Nowhere near as good as the first one.

When Hollywood creators complained that online reviews was hurting the industry, both critic's and fans loudly replied... Then Stop making bad movies!

Nothing could be closer to that truth then Frozen 2. Whilst the animator s can hold their heads high in accomplishing their role with some dignity, everything else was cheap and tacky.  

One of the worst musical scores of this generation had me checking the time periodically and only a handful of well placed jokes kept me from ignoring the overly predictable story line. 

Even for a family movie, it's dull character growth and self plagiarism of the original movie is more than I can tolerate from a high budget film.
The movie is good. Good graphics with good animations and voice but the story does have anything new in it.

Frozen II is a deeper and darker story than its predecessor and that is not a bad thing with this beautifully animated sequel. The story is not only enchanting and makes for great viewing, but it also enriches the way you view the first film as well. The songs are more mature in nature and may not be as ear catching as "Let it go", though with some repetitive viewings they might make their way into your Disney playlist. All in all, this is a worthy sequel to a movie that really didn't need one. But, after seeing it, you will be glad it did.
